ability_effect(vital_spirit, defensive, passive, [combat_relevance-mixed, condition-always_active, confidence-0.8, domain-status, empower_state-true, has_overworld_component-true, source-auto_marker, trigger-passive], 'Modelagem automatica por marcadores: This Pokémon cannot be asleep. This causes rest to fail altogether. If a Pokémon is asleep and acquires this ability, it will immediately wake up; this includes when regaining a lost ability upon leaving battle. This ability functions identically to insomnia in battle. Overworld: If the lead Pokémon has this ability, higher-levelled Pokémon have their encounter rate increased.').
ability_effect(volt_absorb, defensive, on_hit, [combat_relevance-combat, condition-electric_interaction, confidence-0.8, empower_state-true, hp_gain_fraction-0.25, source-auto_marker, trigger-on_hit, type_hint-electric, type_hint-ground], 'Modelagem automatica por marcadores: Whenever an electric-type move hits this Pokémon, it heals for 1/4 of its maximum HP, negating any other effect on it. This ability will not take effect if this Pokémon is ground-type and thus immune to Electric moves. Electric moves will ignore this Pokémon''s substitute. This effect includes non-damaging moves, i.e. thunder wave.').
